"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-03-19-paris-olympics-lifts-intimacy-ban-seeks-300000-condoms\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics will be doing away with one of the rule changes introduced during the previous Summer Games in Tokyo back in \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009921.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 119, \"end\": 124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998844254561532, \"rank\": 9.454693469563298e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo Games introduced an intimacy ban in light of the breakout of the COVID-19 virus, preventing athletes from getting into close contact, including hugs and handshakes, and were even asked to avoid singing and chanting.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19\", \"score\": 0.6929335083104706, \"rank\": 0.4430851147115884, \"text\": \"COVID-19\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those guidelines will not be in place during the event in Paris, and the Olympic village will be supplied with a staggering 300,000 condoms for the Games, according toSky News.\\u00c2\\u00a0Roughly 14,250 people are anticipated to reside in the village, including 9,000 athletes.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999975527046377, \"rank\": 2.4473012695927444e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics will run from July 26 through Aug. 11, 2024.\\u00c2  In Tokyo, athletes were asked to wear masks and undergo periodic health checks.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998844254561532, \"rank\": 9.454693469563298e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the intimacy rules that were in place in 2021, 150,000 condoms were distributed at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those rules will be pushed to the wayside in \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009924 following last year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s declaration of the end of the global COVID-19 health emergency by the World Health Organization.\\u00c2  This year, the Olympic village will be housed in the French capital, located roughly four miles north of the city center.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9865562873032363, \"rank\": 0.009902320240622351, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Included in the village will be a sports bar or \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cVillage Club,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d though it will not serve alcohol.\\u00c2  Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1320, \"